trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls used to provide catalogs of Web server controls that end users can add to a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller som brukes til å gi kataloger for webserverkontroller sluttbrukere kan legge til en webside.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogPartCollection class is a read-only collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, typically used by a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone to track the set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls contained by the zone.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CatalogPartCollection er en skrivebeskyttet samling <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, som vanligvis brukes av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone for å spore sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollene som finnes i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: When a Web Parts page enters catalog mode, the zone creates a new CatalogPartCollection object consisting of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Når en webdeler side angir katalogmodus, sonen oppretter et nytt CatalogPartCollection-objekt som består av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control in the collection can contain references to zero or more Web server controls, which are displayed in the form of a catalog of available server controls.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen i samlingen kan inneholde referanser til null eller flere server webkontroller, som vises i form av en katalog med tilgjengelige serverkontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: You can create a CatalogPartCollection collection of controls for your own programmatic use if, for example, you need to perform some mass operation on a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Du kan opprette en CatalogPartCollection samling kontroller for programmatisk Bruk Hvis for eksempel må du utføre noen for operasjonen på et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Even though the CatalogPartCollection object is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Selv om CatalogPartCollection-objektet er skrivebeskyttet, kan du endre programmatisk underliggende kontrollene som det refereres til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new, empty instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny, tom forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogPartCollection constructor initializes an empty instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CatalogPartCollection initialiserer en tom forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This overload of the constructor is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> class in its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A> method to create an empty collection object.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren-overlasten er brukt internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>klasse i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A>metode for å opprette en tom samling-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone then creates instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls declared in the child zone template, and uses an internal method of the collection to add them.
trans-unit.target: Sonen deretter opprettes forekomster av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller deklarert i malen underordnede sone og bruker en intern metoden i samlingen til å legge dem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: You cannot use this overload of the CatalogPartCollection constructor to create a new instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> and add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to it.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke bruke denne overlasten CatalogPartCollection-konstruktøren for å opprette en ny forekomst av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>og legge til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller til det.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: You must use one of the other overloads for the CatalogPartCollection constructor instead.
trans-unit.target: Du må bruke en annen overlastingene for CatalogPartCollection konstruktøren i stedet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"></xref> class by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"> </xref> klasse ved å sende i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The CatalogPartCollection constructor initializes an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> class and passes in a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CatalogPartCollection initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>klassen og formidler i en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This is one overload of the CatalogPartCollection constructor that you can use to create a new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object and add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to it.
trans-unit.target: Dette er én overbelastning av CatalogPartCollection konstruktøren som du kan bruke til å opprette en ny <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>objekt, og Legg til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller til det.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> instance created by the constructor is read-only, you can still access the individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the collection programmatically and call their properties and methods.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>forekomster opprettet i konstruktøren er skrivebeskyttet, kan du fortsatt tilgang til individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollerer i samlingen programmatisk og kall sine egenskaper og metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: One common scenario for using this constructor would be if you want to perform some batch operation on an entire set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, such as changing the content, appearance, or position of a related group of items.
trans-unit.target: Er en vanlig scenario for å bruke denne konstruktøren Hvis du vil utføre en bunke-operasjon på en hele settet med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, for eksempel endre innhold, utseendet eller plasseringen av en beslektet gruppe elementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"></xref> class by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of the existing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls in a zone, and an additional collection of controls.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"> </xref> klasse ved å sende i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling av den eksisterende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller i en sone, og en ekstra samling av kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of existing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls in a zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>for eksisterende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller i en sone.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of additional <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>for ekstra <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular control exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om en bestemt kontroll finnes i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to determine whether a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> object is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains kan du bestemme om en bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>objektet er en del av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> som er merket av for å finne ut om den er i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular control is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om en bestemt kontroll i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object, or a subset of those controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du ønsker å sette sammen en egendefinert matrise kan inneholde den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>-objekt eller et delsett av kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> objekter kan inneholde kopierte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Startpunktet i matrisen som skal plasseres samlingen innholdet.

trans-unit.source: References a static, read-only, empty instance of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Refererer til en statisk skrivebeskyttet, tom forekomst av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A static, read-only, empty instance of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> reduces memory usage in cases where you want an empty collection instance to return the proper object type from a method or to compare the instance with another object, but you do not need to add members to the instance.
trans-unit.target: En statisk skrivebeskyttet, tom forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>reduserer minnebruk i tilfeller der du vil bruke en tom samling forekomst til å returnere riktig objekttypen fra en annen metode, eller til å sammenligne forekomst med et annet objekt, men du trenger ikke å legge til medlemmer i forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer posisjonen for en bestemt medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls on a Web Parts page, and you need to locate a particular control in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf er nyttig hvis du har flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en webdeler, og du trenger å finne en bestemt kontroll i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> that is a member of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> som medlem av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a member of the collection, based on its position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et medlem i samlingen, basert på plasseringen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer allows you to access the underlying <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object by index, and change their property values or call methods.
trans-unit.target: Indeksering for elementet får du tilgang til den underliggende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>objekt av indeksen, og endre egenskapsverdiene eller kalle metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on a unique string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et medlem i samlingen basert på en unik streng-identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer allows you to access the underlying <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object by use of a string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Elementet indeksering får du tilgang til den underliggende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>objektet ved hjelp av en streng-identifikator.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection> object is read-only, you can change the property values or call methods on the underlying controls accessed by the indexer.
trans-unit.target: Selv om det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>objektet er skrivebeskyttet, kan du endre egenskapsverdiene eller kalle metoder på underliggende Kontroller åpnes av indeksering.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> i en samling.

trans-unit.source: The first in the collection whose ID equals the value of id.
trans-unit.target: Først med IDen er lik verdien i samlingen id .
